@page "/Faq"

<MudContainer>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.h2" Color="Color.Primary">Frequently asked questions</MudText>
    <MudExpansionPanels>
        <MudExpansionPanel Text="What is 'popularity'?">
            <p>
                Popularity is a lifetime score, that is generated by the API from TMDB.
            </p>
            <p>
                It is constantly changing as users interact with the sites, therefore you might
                see that an actors most popular movie changes as time goes by.
            </p>
            <p>The actions that influences the score are different for each type.</p>
            <br/>
            <h3>Movies</h3>
            <ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 16px">
                <li>Number of votes for the day</li>
                <li>Number of views for the day</li>
                <li>Number of users who marked it as a "favourite" for the day</li>
                <li>Release date</li>
                <li>Number of total votes</li>
                <li>Previous days score</li>
            </ul>
            <br/>
            <h3>Celebs</h3>
            <ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 16px">
                <li>Number of views for the day</li>
                <li>Previous days score</li>
            </ul>
        </MudExpansionPanel>
    </MudExpansionPanels>
</MudContainer>

